<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta name="description" content="Frequently asked questions about bStats.">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
    <title>bStats - FAQ</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/stylesheets/tailwind.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen"/>
    <link href="/stylesheets/style.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen"/>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-100 antialiased">

<% include ../templates/navigation.ejs %>

<main>
    <section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-20 bg-slate-950"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 hero-noise opacity-30"></div>
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-24 sm:py-28">
            <header class="space-y-6 text-center">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-white/20 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/70">FAQ</span>
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-5xl">Frequently asked questions</h1>
                <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">Quick answers for the things we get asked the most. Need something else? Ping us on Discord or GitHub.</p>
            </header>

            <div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
                <section class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-slate-950/40 backdrop-blur">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">General</h2>
                    <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
                        <details class="faq-item">
                            <summary class="faq-question">Will bStats stay free?</summary>
                            <p class="faq-answer">Yes. The service is funded by GameHosting and donations from the community. If we ever add optional paid perks we’ll keep the core analytics free.</p>
                        </details>
                        <details class="faq-item">
                            <summary class="faq-question">Why isn’t there a “Universal” platform?</summary>
                            <p class="faq-answer">Cross-posting a plugin to a single “Universal” category would double-count players and servers. Keeping each platform separate keeps the stats honest.</p>
                        </details>
                        <details class="faq-item">
                            <summary class="faq-question">Is there an API?</summary>
                            <p class="faq-answer">Yes! The REST API is documented at <a href="/help/rest-api" class="accent-text hover:opacity-80">/help/rest-api</a>. You can fetch plugin info, charts, and raw data.</p>
                        </details>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-slate-950/40 backdrop-blur">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Accounts</h2>
                    <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
                        <details class="faq-item">
                            <summary class="faq-question">How do I change my password?</summary>
                            <p class="faq-answer">At the moment you need to contact the maintainers. If your account is compromised, let us know immediately and we’ll help you reset it.</p>
                        </details>
                        <details class="faq-item">
                            <summary class="faq-question">I forgot my password!</summary>
                            <p class="faq-answer">Drop us a message on Discord or open an issue on GitHub with proof of ownership. We’ll reset the account manually for now.</p>
                        </details>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-slate-950/40 backdrop-blur">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Metrics class</h2>
                    <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
                        <details class="faq-item">
                            <summary class="faq-question">How do I add bStats to my plugin?</summary>
                            <p class="faq-answer">Follow the walkthrough in our <a href="/getting-started/include-metrics" class="accent-text hover:opacity-80">integration guide</a>. It covers Maven shading and the single-file drop-in.</p>
                        </details>
                        <details class="faq-item">
                            <summary class="faq-question">Where can I report bugs or request features?</summary>
                            <p class="faq-answer">Use GitHub. Website-related issues live at <a href="https://github.com/Bastian/bStats/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="accent-text hover:opacity-80">github.com/Bastian/bStats</a>. Metrics class issues belong in <a href="https://github.com/Bastian/bStats-Metrics/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="accent-text hover:opacity-80">github.com/Bastian/bStats-Metrics</a>.</p>
                        </details>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<% include ../templates/footer.ejs %>
<% include ../templates/globalScripts.ejs %>

</body>
</html>
